# Web3Auth (MetaMask Embedded Wallets) — free client ID for social login.
# Get one at https://dashboard.web3auth.io (Sapphire Devnet, EVM).
# Public value, safe to expose. Leave empty to use AvaKit's bundled demo key
# (works on localhost only) — set your own before deploying to a real domain.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3AUTH_CLIENT_ID=
